tc.)</li> <li>Amazon web services: S3, EMR, Redshift</li> <li>Strong understanding of SQL and underlying technologies</li> <li>Machine learning experience and/or visualization chops (D3, etc.) is a big plus</li> <br /><br /></ul><strong>Benefits<br /></strong><ul> <li>Become a significant stakeholder in the business as part of your compensation package.</li> <li>Work with repeat entrepreneurs with a track record of success.</li> <li>Receive top health insurance benefits.</li></ul></div><div class="rich-text" itemprop="description">Simon is a tool that transforms your data into clear insights that let you get more out of your marketing. Connect your data in minutes, create customized segments, deploy to existing channels, and discover what your customers want.</div>